.name
Badger
.type
Reminder program
.short
Reminds you of outstanding events on start-up
.description
Reminder program for your startup-sequence.  Badger will
open a window and display any important events that are 
'due'.  Badger will not bother you if there is nothing to
report.  Events are entered via menu and prompts.  This
is version 2.05a, an update to version 2.01e on disk 432.
Includes many new features such as event editing and
automatic holiday notification.
.version
2.05a
